<html>
<head>
  <title>Account Deletion Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Account Deletion Confirmation</h2>
  <p>Dear <%= data.name %>,</p>
  
  <p>We regret to inform you that your account with <%= data.company %> has been deleted. This decision was made as per your request received on <%= data.deletionDate %>. We understand that circumstances may have led you to this decision, and we respect your choice.</p>
  
  <p>Please note that the deletion process is irreversible, and all data associated with your account has been permanently removed from our systems. This includes your personal information, login credentials, transaction history, and any other data you may have stored within your account.</p>
  
  <p>As a result of this deletion, you will no longer have access to the services, features, and benefits provided by <%= data.company %>. Any ongoing subscriptions or memberships associated with your account have been terminated, and you will no longer receive any communication or updates from us.</p>
  
  <p>If you believe this account deletion was made in error or have any concerns regarding your decision, please don't hesitate to reach out to our customer support team at <%= data.company %>. They will be more than happy to assist you with any inquiries or provide further clarification regarding this matter.</p>
  
  <p>We appreciate the time you spent as a valued member of our community and hope that our services have met your expectations during your tenure with us. If circumstances change in the future and you decide to rejoin our platform, we would be delighted to welcome you back.</p>
  
  <p>Thank you for your understanding, and we wish you all the best in your future endeavors.</p>
  
  <p>Sincerely,</p>
  <p>Team from</p>
  <p><%= data.company %></p>
</body>
</html>
